---
title: Steak and Montreal Spiced Shrimp with Grilled Zucchini and Heirloom Tomatoes
description: In this upside-down surf and turf meal shrimp is coated in peppery Montreal steak spice, while juicy steak gets a pat of garlic butter.  A fresh summer salad of zucchini and tomatoes balances out this heavy hitter!
